data.name: grdResult.QuerySQL
data.value:
SELECT DISTINCT 'O2' RECODE_GUBUN , 'BML ' CENTER_CODE , :f_request_key , A.HANGMOG_CODE HANGMOG_CODE , C.JANGBI_OUT_CODE SRL_CODE , C.SPECIMEN_CODE SPECIMEN_CODE , C.EMERGENCY EMERGENCY , ' ' , A.SPECIMEN_SER , C.JUNDAL_GUBUN_NAME , A.LAB_NO , A.CPL_RESULT , A.STANDARD_YN , A.COMMENTS , NVL(A.VITROS,'N') /*결과로드여부를 관리*/ , A.RESULT_YN , C.GUMSA_NAME , FN_CPL_CODE_NAME('04',C.SPECIMEN_CODE) SPECIMEN_NAME FROM CPL0101 C, CPL3020 A, CPL2010 B WHERE B.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND B.JUBSU_DATE = TO_DATE('20'||SUBSTR(:f_request_key,1,6)) AND B.JUBSU_TIME = SUBSTR(:f_request_key,7,4) AND B.BUNHO = SUBSTR(:f_request_key,11) AND A.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND A.FKCPL2010 = B.PKCPL2010 AND C.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND C.HANGMOG_CODE = A.HANGMOG_CODE AND C.SPECIMEN_CODE = A.SPECIMEN_CODE AND C.EMERGENCY = A.EMERGENCY -- AND A.HANGMOG_CODE < '05001' /* 세포진 빼기 */ -- AND C.SLIP_CODE <> '27S' /* 일반검사 빼기 */ AND C.UITAK_CODE = 'BML' --BML일반
ORDER BY A.LAB_NO, A.HANGMOG_CODE

data.name: grdHangmog.QuerySQL
data.value:
SELECT 'O2' RECODE_GUBUN , 'SAN ' CENTER_CODE , TO_CHAR(A.PART_JUBSU_DATE,'YYMMDD')||A.PART_JUBSU_TIME||A.BUNHO REQUEST_KEY , ' ' HOSPITAL_CODE , B.HANGMOG_CODE HANGMOG_CODE , C.JANGBI_OUT_CODE SAN_CODE , SUBSTR(C.JANGBI_OUT_CODE,5,2) SPECIMEN_CODE --, C.EMERGENCY EMERGENCY , DECODE(FN_CPL_SPECIMEN_PRN_YN(A.IN_OUT_GUBUN, A.FKOCS1003, A.FKOCS2003), 'X', 'Y', 'N') EMERGENCY , ' ' , B.SPECIMEN_SER , C.JUNDAL_GUBUN_NAME , C.GUMSA_NAME , FN_CPL_CODE_NAME('04',C.SPECIMEN_CODE) SPECIMEN_NAME FROM CPL0101 C, CPL3020 B, CPL2010 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.PART_JUBSU_DATE = TO_DATE('20'||SUBSTR(:f_request_key,1,6)) AND A.PART_JUBSU_TIME = SUBSTR(:f_request_key,7,4) AND A.BUNHO = SUBSTR(:f_request_key,11) AND A.PART_JUBSU_DATE IS NOT NULL AND B.HOSP_CODE = A.HOSP_CODE AND B.FKCPL2010 = A.PKCPL2010 AND B.SPECIMEN_SER = A.SPECIMEN_SER AND C.HOSP_CODE = B.HOSP_CODE AND C.HANGMOG_CODE = B.HANGMOG_CODE AND C.SPECIMEN_CODE = B.SPECIMEN_CODE AND C.EMERGENCY = B.EMERGENCY AND NVL(C.CHUBANG_YN,'Y') = 'Y' /* 자식 항목들은 의뢰하지 않는다 */ AND C.UITAK_CODE = '01' AND C.JANGBI_OUT_CODE IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY B.SPECIMEN_SER,B.PKCPL3020
